$ System.TypeLoadException (class)

A `System.TypeLoadException` is thrown when the → Microsoft/dot-net/Common-Language-Runtime[CLR] cannot
  • locate an → Microsoft/dot-net/assembly,
  • find a type within an assembly or
  • load a type.

`TypeLoadException` inherits from → Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/SystemException[`System.SystemException`].

`TypeLoadException` is associated with `HRESULT COR_E_TYPELOAD` whose value is 0x80131522.
